  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.inject.Provider<javafx.scene.transform.Affine>, IAdaptable.Bound<IVisualPart<? extends javafx.scene.Node>>

    public class TransformProvider
extends IAdaptable.Bound.Impl<IVisualPart<? extends javafx.scene.Node>>
implements Provider<javafx.scene.transform.Affine>
    The TransformProvider can be registered on an IVisualPart to insert an Affine into its visual's transformations list and access that Affine. Per default, this Affine is manipulated to relocate or transform an IVisualPart.
